  "text": "In addition to the usual Frobenius norm, family of Bregman divergences-which Frobenius norm and Kullback-Leibler divergence are part of it-can also be used as the distance measures. Detailed discussion on Bregman divergences can be found in, e.g., ref. [CITATION_1] . In this work, we will consider only Frobenius norm.",
